decks.notes: The deck is focused on utilizing the prowess ability of Adeliz, The Cinder Wind to build a powerful aggro strategy. The deck includes a combination of cheap and efficient spells, creatures, and burn spells to quickly overwhelm the opponent. With cards like Stormwing Entity, Sprite Dragon, and prowess triggers from spells like Lava Dart and Wizard's Lightning, the deck aims to deal damage quickly and efficiently. Counterspells like Force of Will and Spell Pierce are included to protect the game plan and disrupt the opponent's strategy. Overall, the key concept of the deck is to apply constant pressure, utilizing Adeliz's ability to pump up the team and close out the game before the opponent can stabilize.
